Stayed here for 1 night. Modern facility with wifi. The room was comfortable, a little small, but nice modern contemporary style. No funny smells. The shower adjusted for height, which is a super bonus for us tall people out there. Didn't give it 5 stars because they could have had some complimentary muffins or cereal at breakfast. I ended up ordering an spinach omelet which was good. Staff was friendly too.

